tats and that there are no other relevant classes. Let's take a closer look.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0c7770d8cb7e365d016a41db9db7808195964e385079cbdc0f\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqQduz85MxkU6UFss9kkjle6oR-g3_t13OMEXqXM4OC4tts9s365H9layOqxHA7KqarK5RBBD3hKm-5Ba-tyjaUAXWMCfUSEFexNFUk9iGVi7Vlf1YwrTub6_OZfA0HQe2D_yBkqX1Z7sJM5Frua3VLG0iQJdplNjTXVKUaEcilR9F3UwVm-vpIXClBDhxJeScC4MMSk-yZlyACG69XT5N6ZP5xF8QWb9XJQmF_doiN4wY4feqYkimvnXkbm_bbtKxrqtJ6fca9DIKgrcX8DRGpl9BT88h1JncyJzAVg3JXf16qt4lj_-F_1xlwDrsxLgJS4ccPhUT7PEJJscwjT96-rhxPOiNDhtKMr4CTVGGHG-X5XNpzzPXRJ7zxbfN3bnhnS5zncg5mvRN7LbSsU_HjMFsVjDr6PnzvhdtFh_dqbXQHUv-Mno6T8SsAojO7LrOgSEdyQzumv9hORwgsNqJgkozkBek60oTHx5W7I82TkURncaAaNI5hzWtmrxNKNnbVs7Fsb3Z8ktp61BsY4Rgqvu-WYKwTBb1mrF3qaHzKpB3ytjB2wwj8BM-AaQKZhgi0MVd1FYhjRkIsACgetuZzQj500PfH7YiYjkphVSpW3VStioorp4We6jRG8egOMzFY60ZEi35AWGhZnZkacF5X6tW9kV5kekhXShNQ2asHTXIhutM3SGfboRGg9TQeGBztW9yjKD24s9LuH_I6eeNiX6Phz-cOKOFoa_5SWDFtx0BSRb4yHphKVTRjyuB3YkYkhjMzXrzgxcUEIl8ywsgLEaaVT1A7gZpglfVOaJbD2PNyfqZT_kEMLTZochk2l9HjREeM0fbdNqBJkUdoCkfUgz4js3KP6twYuZdZEaJogetkQrQf7qpkYjrVvhDQJem7KxLaQd8j1cFcXmWY9bbyAyAZsVbbNEOa4cXfyzFivtiIlEDvuhMmPqFSEMxGl40WiFVTyW4nsIFMvLR_eOPt7SoR05zEw65iL7aTRv3VgzDIsWChlR7NxAnsCaO9bNX4DeQ_hmoa3ZCO2-KR1W7ZDsJPuIJFnSL_eym_LKeBAzYTEPo-E_grteiF_QQarg6hdbvRbYSOU32YTYA7Argn5zQxkckdoB8BDiCm-MSHnteUDU22RUcdHFWUsNZG6wTo0RwsHV4TUeYHmUEg-7JdHqHSxmt-0TLRLu4vh9reSlBE-R3g_JtnS8thvEJZZFOAjKaoGI5PH7pP6RjOdgRQ1FPpwbkjH3RGmg-PlGNTFRSdIw9yY0Y7vk-M-rpPrwwqx-o1Jrr52p5kjUHSdvbgN1Oz-csv3VyV4RR9pAWqR_KxKP2sfASeGZ_5hEIv0s47ybKdKR5NQ1nW-WqJF7Nqwvle4dQp1yHF3XDkR91ZSna4ALBTF9a9MnIdaRTtdcWc94Pg74Sbg9ZhrxC3XRZW9OFuB9_nFPiX1_il0xX1HZAZyAxNoHzX22Ux_WjlbkNVhJ5uvwde106M3c2NE-mBAPP_0pe0_4n_kDfb-qlOpd_P9ryg_pCVKUGQeZR2Eur7oLBJwQgCDwnEZ-7nNZlj8lmeCOboEjOVhOOwwHHqqgbtGAWfQoNK5czzBUZsi7-CpZETXw-YSUKchQADAuCSbDsb-Q875FRgziSdhiAXmZulZ7qlulGFdKLOXhWoyhXVrYkah9PiGZoOqAb4Rn9oLCp5phuKM_ZnuZ3TLiFSzDJDCCysI54-fAaVpKjh_h6CLU6rZxz-AbnKDkw8opm6KZXtwkswWy-61k